* Iron Raptor snarled under her breath and let one of her arms fall to the 
side and then brought it up behind her armored back, motioning with her hand 
for AzureBlade to keep his tongue within his mouth at this point in time.
The last thing they needed was for either party to get hotheaded and if this 
Devil Gigatron kept up his " High and mighty" attutude, AzureBlade wouldn't 
be the only Maximal present that needed to be reminded to keep their cool.
Iron cleared her throat.*

" To business. You want peace? How do you plan to get it?"

* The Maximals had tried FOREVER to bring peace...even fallen into traps for 
the sake of a warless world. Exactly how could this bot hope to achieve it 
if they could not?*

............................................

* Diana mewed in protest as she rebounded from AzureBlade's foot and skidded 
to a stop in a cloud of dust, flat on her tail and sitting up.
She blinked a few times as the dust cleared and twitched her whiskers, 
completely at a loss for action.*

" Ow...."

* Fur ruffled and paws sore she sat, rubbing at the sore spot in the center 
of her head.*
